<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Sankalpa</title>
    <link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.json">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#667eea">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/icons/icon-192x192.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6733c6, #f757a7);
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            color: white;
        }

        /* Navigation Bar */
        .nav-bar {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            animation: slideDown 0.5s ease forwards;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .nav-links img {
            height: 45px;
            width: auto;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-links img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .other-links {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .other-links a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 25px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .other-links a:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        /* Dropdown Styles */
        .dropdown {
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .dropbtn {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 25px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        }

        .dropbtn:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .dropdown-content {
            display: none;
            position: absolute;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            min-width: 160px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            z-index: 1000;
            border-radius: 15px;
            top: 100%;
            right: 0;
            margin-top: 5px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .dropdown-content a {
            color: #333 !important;
            padding: 10px 14px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: block;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin: 5px;
            background: transparent !important;
            border: none !important;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .dropdown-content a:hover {
            background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1) !important;
            transform: none;
            box-shadow: none;
        }

        .dropdown:hover .dropdown-content {
            display: block;
            animation: fadeInDown 0.3s ease forwards;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 5rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #e0e7ff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .hero h2 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            opacity: 0.9;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        /* User Type Section */
        .user-type-section {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .user-type-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 1.8rem;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards;
            min-height: auto;
        }

        .user-type-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px) scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        }

        .user-type-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .user-type-card > p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .features-preview {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .features-preview span {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
            padding: 0.2rem 0;
            border-left: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            padding-left: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .features-preview span:hover {
            opacity: 1;
            border-left-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }

        /* General CTA Section */
        .general-cta {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            padding-top: 1rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        /* CTA Buttons */
        .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.8rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            min-width: 130px;
            text-align: center;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .btn::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2), transparent);
            transition: left 0.5s;
        }

        .btn:hover::before {
            left: 100%;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5, #7c3aed);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.03);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.4);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5b52f0, #8b46f7);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            color: white;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
            transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.03);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }

        .general-cta .btn-secondary {
            font-size: 1rem;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981, #059669);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
            border: none;
        }

        .general-cta .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #34d399, #10b981);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes slideDown {
            from {
                transform: translateY(-100%);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                transform: translateY(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: translateY(0px);
            }
            50% {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }
        }

        /* Smooth scrolling */
        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .user-type-section {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                max-width: 500px;
            }
            
            .hero {
                padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-bar {
                padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 0.8rem;
            }
            
            .other-links {
                gap: 0.8rem;
            }
            
            .hero {
                padding: 1rem 1rem;
                margin: 15px auto;
            }
            
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .hero h2 {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }
            
            .hero p {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            }

            .user-type-card {
                padding: 1.5rem 1.2rem;
            }

            .user-type-section {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 1.2rem;
                margin: 1.5rem 0;
            }
            
            .cta-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 0.8rem;
            }
            
            .btn {
                min-width: 160px;
            }

            .features-preview {
                text-align: center;
            }

            .dropdown-content {
                right: auto;
                left: 0;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
            
            .hero h2 {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            
            .other-links a, .dropbtn {
                padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem;
                font-size: 0.8rem;
            }
            
            .nav-links img {
                height: 32px;
            }

            .user-type-card {
                padding: 1.2rem 1rem;
            }

            .user-type-card h3 {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }

            .btn {
                padding: 0.7rem 1.2rem;
                font-size: 0.85rem;
                min-width: 140px;
            }

            .user-type-section {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 1rem;
                margin: 1rem 0;
            }
            
            .hero {
                padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
                margin: 10px auto;
            }
        }

        /* Ensure everything fits in viewport */
        @media (max-height: 800px) {
            .hero {
                margin: 10px auto;
                padding: 1rem 2rem;
            }
            
            .user-type-card {
                padding: 1.2rem;
            }
            
            .general-cta {
                margin-top: 1rem;
            }
        }

        @media (max-height: 600px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
                margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            }
            
            .hero h2 {
                font-size: 1rem;
                margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
            }
            
            .hero p {
                font-size: 0.85rem;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
            }
            
            .user-type-card {
                padding: 1rem;
            }
            
            .user-type-section {
                gap: 1rem;
                margin: 1rem 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="nav-bar">
        <div class="nav-links">
            <img src="/static/sankalpa.png" alt="Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="other-links">
            <a href="/about" class="about">About us</a>
            <div class="dropdown">
                <button class="dropbtn">Login</button>
                <div class="dropdown-content">
                    <a href="/login/customer">Customer</a>
                    <a href="/login/agent">Agent</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="dropdown">
                <button class="dropbtn">Sign Up</button>
                <div class="dropdown-content">
                    <a href="/register/customer">Customer</a>
                    <a href="/register/agent">Agent</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero">         
        <h1>Sankalpa</h1>         
        <h2>Welcome to the Future of Financial Intelligence.</h2>
        <p>Sankalpa is a next-gen AI platform that helps you with smart policy suggestions, personalized upselling, interactive simulator games with helpful nudges, and an emotion aware TIA assistant that can connect you to call support so you can make quick, confident, and secure financial choices.</p>       
        
        <div class="user-type-section">
            <div class="user-type-card">
                <h3>For Customers</h3>
                <p>Personalized financial insights, multilingual support, and interactive tools</p>
                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <a href="/register/customer" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
                    <a href="/login/customer" class="btn btn-secondary">Customer Login</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="user-type-card">
                <h3>For Agents</h3>
                <p>Advanced analytics dashboard and engagement tracking tools</p>
                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <a href="/register/agent" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
                    <a href="/login/agent" class="btn btn-secondary">Agent Login</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="general-cta">
            <a href="" class="btn btn-secondary">Get Mobile App</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
